Title: Nothing to Declare
Writer: Dany Boon (scenario and dialogue), Yaël Boon (collaboration)
Actors: Benoît Poelvoorde, Dany Boon, Christel Pedrinelli, Karin Viard
Plot: A Belge-Francophobe customs officer is forced to team up with a Frenchman during the elimination of the Franco-Belge borders in the 90s.
Production: Les Productions du Ch'timi, TF1 Films Production, Pathé
